						               													<description>Manage your own dreamliner! Passengers come aboard to experience the holidays of their dreams. Your job as the manager of the ship is to make their dreams come true. Some want to go sightseeing; others want to do sports; some simply want to relax, while yet others are looking for inspirational experiences&amp;hellip;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;To please them all, add upgrades to your ship, plan activities and look for the right cities to head for. When you make passengers happy, they will reward you with points. And that is the only thing that counts at the end!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Each round starts with you choosing a destination you want to head for with your ship. Then you draft 2 paired cards. These can be upgrades for your ship or activities. Once you have them, you can build these upgrades into your ship or use the activity cards to fulfil the desires of your passengers. Every time you do that, the happy passenger leaves your ship, giving you points. You replace them with new passengers with different needs. The game ends when there are no passengers left. Whoever scores the most points is the winner.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
